text: Jacquelina Alvarez (born 21 August 1989) is an Argentine professional racing cyclist. She rides for the Lotto-Soudal Ladies team. ==See also== * List of 2015 UCI Women's Teams and riders ==References== ==External links== * Category:1989 births Category:Living people Category:Argentine female cyclists Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
